{"id": "1511647918438875296", "channel_id": "1511647918438875296", "type": 0, "author_id": "996022998786125885", "author_name": "pleaseineedabf", "author_bot": false, "content": "Been playing for a few days, mindlessly pulling on standard banner. I've been running uvhash leigh faint aigis and being low hp to meet uvhash dmg requirements is too cumbersome. \n\nAround start of chapter 4, and heard it's where difficulty starts to rise, so would like to run another team that's a little safer. \n\n+ also would like to know some banner priorities, if any. Been pulling titans blade and its currently e2. Not sure whether to continue getting it to +12 or pull for characters first.", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T08:29:08.816000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-03T08:29:32.857000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1511647918887796848", "filename": "Screenshot_20260603-161842.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 202506, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1511647918438875296/1511647918887796848/Screenshot_20260603-161842.jpg?ex=6a21e014&is=6a208e94&hm=fd3a4a679b5d1d8719ed9d122ee690c914bbfdd2492a1dd4f876a0bb3f547443&"}, {"id": "1511647919571206245", "filename": "Screenshot_20260603-161853.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 204473, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1511647918438875296/1511647919571206245/Screenshot_20260603-161853.jpg?ex=6a21e015&is=6a208e95&hm=2e3a6e85d20cb27f57304676ca5fde3d32c634ba3c0a104db5a0012c4920d0b6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1511647918438875296", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team building help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1511648229391990935", "channel_id": "1511647918438875296", "type": 0, "author_id": "996022998786125885", "author_name": "pleaseineedabf", "author_bot": false, "content": "tried out doresain, but I've noticed he seems to need to kill mobs to get his special card? not sure if im correct about that, maybe im just playing him bad", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T08:30:22.953000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1511647918438875296", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team building help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1511680692570947625", "channel_id": "1511647918438875296", "type": 0, "author_id": "454460756721795102", "author_name": "marshadow0398", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm not good at team building and I'm also relatively new player, but I'd pulling for characters first. Also, you already have really good awakeners, like GDoll? Gmurphy (in some tier lists the best dd in the game)? Try Aeqour team - especially adding normal Murphy - her ult reduce enemy damage for 50% for one turn and it really helps when you go through normal story chapters at the beginning - just ult her before strong incoming damage. IMO, Aeqor team is the easiest to go through Arc 1 story chapters, even if it's a bit slow - I was able to finish all Arc 1 chapters (except final battle) with Aequor team only", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T10:39:22.778000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "perfect", "emoji_id": "1356084498630053979", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1511647918438875296", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team building help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"]}
